graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Initialize Components]
    B --> C{Receive Print Job?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Parse Job Details]
    D --> E{Job Valid?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Add Job to Queue]
    E -->|No| G[Display Error Message]
    F --> H{Queue Full?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Discard Job & Notify]
    H -->|No| J[Activate Print Task]
