    Q --> K
    N -->|No Error| R[Continue Printing]
    R --> K
    M --> S{Idle for Long?}
    S -->|Yes| T[Enter Power Saver Mode]
    S -->|No| U[Remain in Idle Mode]
    T --> V{Resume Button Pressed?}
